title: Stats 140XP Project
text:
My group has been working with LA crime data to answer the following research questions:

Can we predict whether a crime is violent or nonviolent from other variables?
Are certain areas more dangerous than other areas?
Does the time of the crime have a significant effect on if the crime is violent or not?

title: Bruin Sports Analytics Project
text: This is an ongoing project where we are trying to create, a Stuff+, Control+, and Pitching+ statistic for the UCLA baseball team.
